title: #92Noon! Russo/Birk/Boudreau/Ledyard/Motzko/JonnyK
description: Russo radio in Denver, Matt Birk finished the first hour on football, Bruce Boudreau gave us the coach's view on tonight's Wild game, John Ledyard debuted as our Senior Bowl correspondent, Gopher coach Bob Motzko on the Border Battle series this weekend, then Jon Krawczynski in studio on hoops & howl!
